  <description><![CDATA[<p>Popular hotel with good service in an excellent location. Situated in the San Rocco area of Livigno just 50 metres from the San Rocco chairlift and 200m from the Carosello 3000 ski lift. The ski bus stops 50m away and the centre of Livigno is a further 900m. The Hotel Alba is a great base from which to enjoy Livigno’s abundance of excellent skiing. Bedrooms have recently been refurbished in a smart and comfortable alpine style.  The hotel is well known for its warm hospitality and the restaurant offers quality Italian fare. </p>]]></description>
